            <title>【CES2025】超轻量宠物追踪器 GlocalMe GPet    打破定位技术限制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=glocalme-gpet</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:37:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GlocalMe GPet]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286240</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 CES 2025 消费科技展，GlocalMe 公司推出全新「GPet」专门为宠物而设，结合云端 SIM 技术与多重定位方式的定位系统。它体积比上代更为细小，超过 200 个国家和地区都可用到无缝定位服务，用户在各种环境下均可保持准确追踪。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>GlocalMe GPet 结合 GPS、AGPS、LBS、WiFi、蓝牙及主动雷达搜寻等六种定位技术，即使在 GPS 和 WiFi 信号不足的密林或室内环境，也可大幅提升定位准确性。云端 SIM 技术支援全球超过 350 个营运商的多网络覆盖，让基站定位精准度提升超过 50%。</p><p>传统追踪装置在最后 100 米的复杂环境中容易出现失误，KeyTracker 则透过主动雷达搜寻功能，即使在无 GPS 的情况下，亦能快速找到目标位置，令各种地形追踪成为可能。</p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>这个 GPet 已内置的云端 SIM 技术免除实体 SIM 卡需求，提供全球连接能力。这款追踪器针对多种需求，包括个人位置保护、物品追踪、宠物防走失及全球无缝网络连接，为日常生活带来更多便利与安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/">【CES2025】超轻量宠物追踪器 GlocalMe GPet    打破定位技术限制</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
