            <title>【CES2025】Lenovo ThinkVision AI 识自己转的芒，识跟踪你、永远显示最佳角度</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkvision-ai/parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-thinkvision-ai</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/lenovo-thinkvision-ai/parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:30:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo ThinkVision AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286154</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今年 CES Lenovo 推出了 ThinkVision AI 功能。这项创新技术能够追踪用户动态，自动调整显示角度，确保用户随时都能以最佳视角欣赏内容，提升观看体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovoai1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovoai1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovoai1-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovoai1.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合 Web Cam 可辨认用家位置，显示最佳角度</p><p>我们的记者 Edward 亲自到场测试过 Lenovo ThinkVision AI，实际体验了该功能的精确度。当用户改变位置时，荧幕能即时追踪并调整显示角度，确保显示效果始终达到最佳状态。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲荧幕会追踪用户位置</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision2-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lenovovision2.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以最佳角度显示内容</p><p>此外 Lenovo ThinkVision P 系列支援串联功能，最多可连接四个显示器，为专业人士提供更大的工作空间。不论是进行数据分析，还是创意设计，都能显著提高工作效率。部分型号支援 True Split 功能，让用户可以将显示器分割为多个虚拟荧幕，从而高效处理多任务，提升工作灵活性。</p><p>ThinkVision P40w 系列支援 Thunderbolt 4 连接，提供更高效的数据传输速度，另外亦支援 Intel AMT（Active Management Technology），让 IT 管理员可更方便远程管理和维护，适合需要多荧幕高效工作流程的企业环境。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
